title: Was Trump at Cheyenne Mountain Military Base Looking at ‘Evidence’ From Pelosi’s Stolen Laptop?
subtitle: Claims that Trump viewed "evidence" on the laptop quickly went viral.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: Pelosi was headed to the "border" but was detained at an undisclosed location due to evidence viewed by President Donald Trump at Cheyenne Mountain military base. The evidence was found on a laptop stolen from her office during the Capitol riot.
